{
  "stem": "10698.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes we were singing-- because we used to go a lot to the Jewish theater.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we also sang songs from the Jewish plays and some Hebrew songs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Please-- you know something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A lot of dates also don't ring bells with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I like-- I talk with my sister today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was talking about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, for God's sakes, I must have blocked a lot of things out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--that they used to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mom had one-- Mom had one Jewish actress that was the most close friend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her name was Barska Fisher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they, they had an, an ad in the paper that a granddaughter is looking for somebody if they knew a Barska Fisher from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, my sister called the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave the, the people the telephone number to call my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this was an open house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, my brother's friends, when it came Purim and Hanukkah, they showered my mom with gifts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they didn't have such open home that they can always come find a meal, find somebody to talk to, spend some time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was the-- and there, and there, there-- always happy, always songs, always so much, so much happiness in the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so was with my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to come home with me from school and do homework with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wipe my nose.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have one here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After all, I got misty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I don't need-- I think that maybe I need it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All that happiness in the house-- always laughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during the time when they closed up the ghetto, my mom used to cook.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't have a maid.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
